Activity Summary: Type of compound activity based on both the MMP readout and the cell viability counter screen.
Ratio Activity: Type of compound activity in the ratio readout of the MMP screen.
Ratio Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal activation in the ratio readout of the MMP screen.
Ratio Efficacy (%): Percent activation in the ratio readout of the MMP screen.
535 nm Activity: Type of compound activity in the 535 nm readout of the MMP screen.
535 nm Potency (uM): he concentration of sample yielding half-maximal activation in the 535 nm readout of the MMP screen.
535 nm Efficacy (%): Type of compound activity in the 535 nm readout of the MMP screen.
590 nm Activity: Type of compound activity in the 590 nm readout of the MMP screen.
590 nm Potency (uM): he concentration of sample yielding half-maximal activation in the 590 nm readout of the MMP screen.
590 nm Efficacy (%): Type of compound activity in the 590 nm readout of the MMP screen.
Viability Activity: Type of compound activity in the cell viability counter screen.
Viability Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of cell viability.
